'''变种剑'''（法語：épée bâtarde，英語：bastard sword），又譯'''混種劍'''或'''杂种剑'''，起源于15或16世纪，一开始是指“不正规的剑或起源不明的剑”，它是“一把既非[[法国|法国]]的、也非[[西班牙|西班牙]]的，也非[[德国|德国]][[國土傭僕|傭兵]]所用的劍，但是比这些大剑都還要长。”<ref>原文''Qui n'étoit ni Françoise , ni Espagnole, ni proprement Lansquenette, mais plus grande que pas une de ces fortes épées''</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=UCY_AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA129&dq=%22%C3%A9p%C3%A9e+b%C3%A2tarde%22&hl=en&ei=PTILTry5HczF8QPo15mJAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CF0Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=%22%C3%A9p%C3%A9e%20b%C3%A2tarde%22&f=false |title=Oeuvres - François Rabelais (écrivain), César de Missy, Jacob Le Duchat, Louis-Fabricius Dubourg, Bernard Picart, Pieter Tanjé, Balthasar Bernaerts, Jacob Folkema - Google Boo... |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107225308/http://books.google.com/books?id=UCY_AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA129&dq=%22%C3%A9p%C3%A9e+b%C3%A2tarde%22&hl=en&ei=PTILTry5HczF8QPo15mJAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CF0Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=%22%C3%A9p%C3%A9e%20b%C3%A2tarde%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref> ''Espée bastarde''也可以指一把有相当长度的，比所有短剑长的剑。<ref name="pbm.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.pbm.com/~lindahl/cotgrave/100small.html |title=Cotgrave's 1611 French/English Dictionary |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053256/http://www.pbm.com/~lindahl/cotgrave/100small.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=ZRcVAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA51&lpg=PA51&dq=espee+bastarde+assez+longuettes&source=bl&ots=kI3TdP3tJK&sig=KoJ1kq9-smA8j76CE9Tkru3Df5s&hl=en&sa=X&ei=GI88Uan8KYrK2AWLloCgCw&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=espee%20bastarde%20assez%20longuettes&f=false |title=Dictionnaire historique de l'ancien langage françois - Sainte-Palaye（Jean-Baptiste它是de La Curne, M. de La Curne de） - Google Books |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408224007/http://books.google.ca/books?id=ZRcVAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA51&lpg=PA51&dq=espee+bastarde+assez+longuettes&source=bl&ots=kI3TdP3tJK&sig=KoJ1kq9-smA8j76CE9Tkru3Df5s&hl=en&sa=X&ei=GI88Uan8KYrK2AWLloCgCw&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=espee%20bastarde%20assez%20longuettes&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

17世紀初期的英國劍術家{{link-en|約瑟夫·史威南|Joseph Swetnam}}说变种剑的长度介于短剑和长剑之间，<ref name="historical-academyii">{{Cite web |url=http://historical-academy.co.uk/blog/2011/07/29/a-perfect-length-ii-the-longsword/ |title=A Perfect Length II: The Longsword – Encased in Steel |access-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203202734/http://historical-academy.co.uk/blog/2011/07/29/a-perfect-length-ii-the-longsword/ |archive-date=2013-12-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>同時期的英國語言學家{{Link-en|朗達爾·寇特葛雷夫|Randle Cotgrave}}的定义也差不多。<ref name="pbm.com"/>

在法语裡，變種劍有時被視同「十字护手刃」（coustille à croix）或「越級劍」（épée de passot）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://littre.fracademic.com/16586/coustil |title=coustil |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408221331/http://littre.fracademic.com/16586/coustil |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=XscWAAAAQAAJ&pg=PR8&lpg=PR8&dq=COUSTILLE+%C3%A0+CROIX&source=bl&ots=VI3i-5z4Rh&sig=6dpXWXSOF5NWxoxiyATnSMMRnLk&hl=en#v=onepage&q=COUSTILLE%20%C3%A0%20CROIX&f=false |title=Les chroniques / Froissart, Jean - Jean Froissart, Jean Alexandre C. Buchon - Google Books |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408224005/http://books.google.ca/books?id=XscWAAAAQAAJ&pg=PR8&lpg=PR8&dq=COUSTILLE+%C3%A0+CROIX&source=bl&ots=VI3i-5z4Rh&sig=6dpXWXSOF5NWxoxiyATnSMMRnLk&hl=en#v=onepage&q=COUSTILLE%20%C3%A0%20CROIX&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=aoIH0RDluwUC&pg=PA116&lpg=PA116&dq=COUSTILLE+%C3%A0+CROIX&source=bl&ots=MeDJ4LApyu&sig=zBO8t2AIre2HI0e1iXS0oAq69qQ&hl=en#v=onepage&q=COUSTILLE%20%C3%A0%20CROIX&f=false |title=Notes and queries - Oxford Journals (Firm) - Google Books |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408212212/http://books.google.ca/books?id=aoIH0RDluwUC&pg=PA116&lpg=PA116&dq=COUSTILLE+%C3%A0+CROIX&source=bl&ots=MeDJ4LApyu&sig=zBO8t2AIre2HI0e1iXS0oAq69qQ&hl=en#v=onepage&q=COUSTILLE%20%C3%A0%20CROIX&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="google1">{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=AYM-AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA129&lpg=PA129&dq=rabelais+longue+epee&source=bl&ots=HSJuYK4SkI&sig=RM3H5K8aEZ_kYWLL3Jqtawgj7DY&hl=en#v=snippet&q=longue%20epee&f=false |title=Dictionnaire étymologique de la langue françoise - Gilles Ménage, Auguste François Jault, Pierre Borel, Pierre de Caseneuve, H. P. Simon de Val-Hébert, Pierre Besnier, Claude ... |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408223435/http://books.google.ca/books?id=AYM-AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA129&lpg=PA129&dq=rabelais+longue+epee&source=bl&ots=HSJuYK4SkI&sig=RM3H5K8aEZ_kYWLL3Jqtawgj7DY&hl=en#v=snippet&q=longue%20epee&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而前者指的是中世纪的专为刺击设计的单手剑；<ref name="google1"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=M2oEAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA116&lpg=PA116&dq=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e+de+passot&source=bl&ots=88ocJfRSOK&sig=etDoOF0XZlpj1hYCKCt9PL-REMw&hl=en#v=onepage&q=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e%20de%20passot&f=false |title=Notes and Queries - Oxford Journals (Firm), William White - Google Books |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408221807/http://books.google.ca/books?id=M2oEAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA116&lpg=PA116&dq=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e+de+passot&source=bl&ots=88ocJfRSOK&sig=etDoOF0XZlpj1hYCKCt9PL-REMw&hl=en#v=onepage&q=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e%20de%20passot&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>而後者則是{{link-en|法兰克弓手|Franc-archer}}（法国、布列塔尼15-16世纪的弓手）的用剑。<ref name="google2">{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=cT28RzoK_YAC&pg=RA1-PA563&lpg=RA1-PA563&dq=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e+de+passot&source=bl&ots=a8zQco4M_c&sig=W15q9fxOFjguzt1LnphjpndC05c&hl=en#v=onepage&q=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e%20de%20passot&f=false |title=Dictionnaire étymologique, critique, historique, anecdotique et littéraire ... - François-Joseph-Michel Noël - Google Books |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408222101/http://books.google.ca/books?id=cT28RzoK_YAC&pg=RA1-PA563&lpg=RA1-PA563&dq=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e+de+passot&source=bl&ots=a8zQco4M_c&sig=W15q9fxOFjguzt1LnphjpndC05c&hl=en#v=onepage&q=%C3%A9p%C3%A9e%20de%20passot&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>passot一字意指它超过了（passaient）正常的短剑长度。<ref name="google2"/> 

德语中称变种剑为「骑马剑」（Reitschwert），<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/explorer/index.php?oid=18930 |title=Fitzwilliam Museum Collections Explorer - Object HEN.M.213-1933（Id:18930） |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408223911/http://www.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/explorer/index.php?oid=18930 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.myarmoury.com/talk/viewtopic.4104.html |title=Patrick Bárta "Bastard" Sword - myArmoury.com |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408224308/http://www.myarmoury.com/talk/viewtopic.4104.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>“文艺复兴早期的變种剑有时也指单手持用的、有复杂护手裝置的武装用剑。一种德国的带有变种风格的护手的武装用剑称为『骑兵剑』（Reitschwert）或『骑士剑』（Degen）。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thearma.org/terms4.htm |title=Sword Forms |access-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613143355/http://www.thearma.org/terms4.htm |archive-date=2017-06-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

